dc_title_s: Current and Historic Simultaneous Conveyances Lincoln County, WI 2018
dc_description_s: This data represents current and historic simultaneous conveyances for Lincoln County, Wisconsin in 2018 and includes the layers 'SimConBndCurent', 'SimConBndHistoric', SimConFrstDivCurrent', 'SimSonFrstDivHistoric', 'SimConSecDivCurrent',and 'SimConSecDivHistoric'.
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison.For access to the most current data available, please visit: http://maps.co.lincoln.wi.us/webapps/gisportal/data.html
